“The SPCA is a MySchool, MyVillage, MyPlanet beneficiary. As are the majority of schools in our amazing city. In a nutshell, their supporters, and in case of the schools, the parents are encouraged to sign up for a MySchool card. Each time they swipe this card they raise funds for the beneficiary close to their hearts,” said Liz Robbertze, MySchool spokesman. This is another initiative brought forth to support the Nelspruit SPCA and to ensure that their food levels reach maximum capacity. The food levels for the various animals at the Nelspruit SPCA.